OL,6,FA woman died after 'complications'
OL,7,Fduring a #2,000 weight loss operation
OL,8,Fin Turkey, an inquest has heard.
OL,10,FLeanne Michelle Leary, from
OL,11,FHollinwood, Greater Manchester, had
OL,12,Fundiagnosed deep vein thrombosis (DVT)
OL,13,Fwhich , the hearing was told.
OL,15,FThe 38-year-old was resuscitated and
OL,16,Frushed to intensive care, but suffered
OL,17,Fa second fatal cardiac arrest the
OL,18,Ffollowing afternoon on 2 July 2023.
