OL,3,CWoman died after 'complications' from
OL,4,Csurgery in Turkey, inquest hears
OL,6,FRochdale Coroners' Court heard Ms
OL,7,FLeary, a mother-of-three, had fallen
OL,8,Fon the stairs at work then complained
OL,9,Fof leg pains after going to Istanbul
OL,10,Fto watch Manchester City in the
OL,11,FChampions League final the month
OL,12,Fbefore her death.
OL,14,FOn her return to the UK she underwent
OL,15,Ftests for DVT, but they were
OL,16,Finconclusive, the inquest heard.
OL,18,FThe compliance manager told her
OL,19,Ffriends she had a 'small blood clot'
OL,20,Fwhich didn't require treatment.
