OL,3,CWoman died after 'complications' from
OL,4,Csurgery in Turkey, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe inquest heard Ms Leary, who had
OL,7,Fasthma and pneumonia, originally
OL,8,Fbooked the gastric sleeve surgery in
OL,9,FApril to take place in October, but
OL,10,Fbrought it forward to July while she
OL,11,Fwas off work sick.
OL,13,FShe did not inform her parents of her
OL,14,Fplans to undergo the #2,000 operation
OL,15,Ffor fear they would try to talk her
OL,16,Fout of it, nor did she discuss it with
OL,17,Fher GP.
