OL,3,CWoman died after 'complications' from
OL,4,Csurgery in Turkey, inquest hears
OL,6,FMs Leary's final text messages to her
OL,7,Fdad, Paul Dermody, as she was about to
OL,8,Fgo into surgery on the morning of 1
OL,9,FJuly, were read out in court.JMs
OL,10,FLeary, who had a BMI of 47, wrote: "I
OL,11,Fdidn't want people to try put me off.
OL,12,FI need this for me and my health."
OL,14,FMr Dermody told the court: "I said I
OL,15,Ffully support what you are doing, but
OL,16,FI want to know where you are every
OL,17,Fstep of the way before and after
OL,18,Fsurgery."JMs Leary's mum, Kathleen
OL,19,FScott, said: "I would have 100 per
OL,20,Fcent talked her out of it. You have to
OL,21,Fthink of the kids.
