OL,6,F"But she felt like there was nothing
OL,7,Fto worry about because she so
OL,8,Fdesperately needed and wanted this
OL,9,Foperation."
OL,11,FWhen, by the next morning, Ms Leary
OL,12,Fhad not responded to a number of texts
OL,13,Fher family began to worry.
OL,15,FA friend contacted the hospital
OL,16,Foutside Istanbul and was told she had
OL,17,Fsuffered a heart attack during surgery.
