OL,3,CWoman died after 'complications' from
OL,4,Csurgery in Turkey, inquest hears
OL,6,FHer parents caught the first flight to
OL,7,FIstanbul, where they were met by an
OL,8,Finterpreter. But on their arrival at
OL,9,Fthe hospital they were given the news
OL,10,Fthat Ms Leary had died.
OL,12,FA post-mortem examination gave the
OL,13,Fcause of death as a pulmonary embolism
OL,14,Fdue to deep vein thrombosis.
OL,16,FPathologist Dr Sami Titi said it was
OL,17,Flikely the DVT was present before Ms
OL,18,FLeary left the UK.
