OL,3,CWoman died after 'complications' from
OL,4,Csurgery in Turkey, inquest hears
OL,6,FHe also said it appeared the hospital
OL,7,Fhad not taken any next of kin details
OL,8,Fin case of an emergency.JCoroner
OL,9,FCatherine McKenna recorded a
OL,10,Fconclusion that Ms Leary had died of
OL,11,F'recognised complications of an
OL,12,Felective surgical procedure combined
OL,13,Fwith underlying medical conditions'.
OL,14,FMs McKenna said: "This case underlines
OL,15,Fthe importance of transparency when it
OL,16,Fcomes to surgical procedures. It is
OL,17,Fimperative to anyone considering a
OL,18,Fprocedure that, irrespective of how
OL,19,Fstraightforward it may seem, all
OL,20,Fsurgery carries risk.
